@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@subscriptionId = replace-me
@callId = replace-me

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/healthz

### List managed subscriptions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/subscriptions

### Force a subscription sync
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/subscriptions/sync

### Reauthorize one subscription
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/subscriptions/{{subscriptionId}}/reauthorize

### Graph webhook validation handshake
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhooks/graph?validationToken=test-token

### Ask the Teams bot to join a meeting by joinWebUrl
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bot/join
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "joinWebUrl": "https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meetup-join/19%3ameeting_example%40thread.v2/0?context=%7B%22Tid%22%3A%2200000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000%22%2C%22Oid%22%3A%2211111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111%22%7D"
}

### List tracked bot calls
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bot/calls

### Leave one tracked call
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bot/calls/{{callId}}/leave

### Register a meeting for compliance enforcement
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/compliance/meetings/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "parentResourceType": "onlineMeeting",
  "parentResourceId": "MsoMeetingId",
  "title": "Quarterly Review",
  "organizerUserId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
  "organizerUpn": "organizer@contoso.com",
  "startedAt": "2026-03-28T15:00:00.000Z",
  "endedAt": "2026-03-28T16:00:00.000Z",
  "expectedArtifacts": {
    "recordingRequired": true,
    "transcriptRequired": true
  },
  "gracePeriodMinutes": 30
}

### List compliance cases
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/compliance/meetings

### Compliance summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/compliance/summary

### Example Teams call callback notification
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhooks/teams/calls
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "value": [
    {
      "resource": "/communications/calls/22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222",
      "resourceData": {
        "callChainId": "33333333-3333-3333-3333-333333333333",
        "state": "terminated",
        "tenantId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
      }
    }
  ]
}

### Example resource notification payload
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhooks/graph
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "validationTokens": [
    "eyJhbGciOiJSUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6IkV4YW1wbGUifQ.example"
  ],
  "value": [
    {
      "subscriptionId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
      "changeType": "created",
      "clientState": "replace-with-long-random-secret",
      "resource": "users/22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222/onlineMeetings('MsoMeetingId')/transcripts('TranscriptId')",
      "tenantId": "33333333-3333-3333-3333-333333333333",
      "resourceData": {
        "id": "TranscriptId",
        "@odata.type": "#Microsoft.Graph.callTranscript"
      },
      "encryptedContent": {
        "data": "base64-ciphertext",
        "dataKey": "base64-key",
        "dataSignature": "base64-signature",
        "encryptionCertificateId": "teams-recordings-webhook-cert"
      }
    }
  ]
}
